1
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:16,280
[How far have you gone with him?]

2
00:00:24,040 --> 00:00:24,960
[Have you slept?]

3
00:00:26,720 --> 00:00:27,440
[When you sleep,]

4
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:29,400
[will these eyes look at him like this?]

5
00:00:31,240 --> 00:00:31,960
Speak!

6
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:34,680
You're bleeding.

7
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:39,520
Why did you save me?

8
00:00:40,160 --> 00:00:41,000
Pang Jingfu,

9
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:43,360
why?

10
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:54,680
Because I'm worried about you.

11
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:02,960
Don't look at anyone like this again.

12
00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:05,960
Do you hear me?

13
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:56,440
You didn't drive me away.

14
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,360
This scene is effective.

15
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,560
We need to hurry up with the secret files.

16
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,760
What's the sound?

17
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,320
The secret room.

18
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,960
Where is the entrance?

19
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,720
What are you doing?

20
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:55,240
I can't sleep.

21
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,000
I want to find a book to read.

22
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:02,440
If that's all you want...

23
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,560
What are you hiding?

24
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:30,160
You said no,

25
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,680
but you wanted it.

26
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,920
You wanted it.

27
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,360
Don't even think about it.

28
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,120
These earrings...

29
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,120
No.

30
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:53,880
These are spy earrings.

31
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,080
Why are you nervous?

32
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:14,480
You're the one

33
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,520
who's nervous.

34
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,360
It's not my first time.

35
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,560
I'm talking about

36
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:32,960
kissing.

37
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,800
This is your first time kissing me.

38
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:40,760
Admit it, Pang Jingfu.

39
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,160
You've already fallen for me.

40
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,000
Soon,

41
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,600
you'll love me.

42
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:19,320
It's a dream.

43
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,360
How could I have such a dream?

44
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,040
Damn it.

45
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:01,960
Let's eat.

46
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,520
[There's a sound in the study.]

47
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,360
[Is there someone]

48
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,440
[in the secret basement?]

49
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:36,000
[I have to find a way to stay here.]

50
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,680
Admit it,

51
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,720
Pang Jingfu.

52
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,520
You've already

53
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,480
taken an interest in me.

54
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:20,760
Yesterday,

55
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:21,680
those killers.

56
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:23,040
I'm afraid they'll come after me again.

57
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:23,520
Can I

58
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:29,400
stay at your place for a few nights?

59
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,320
It won't be long

60
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,480
before you fall in love with me.

61
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:34,920
No.

62
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:36,760
Just...

63
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:37,800
Just a few days.

64
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,440
This isn't a hotel,

65
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,680
and I'm not your bodyguard.

66
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,960
I've saved your number with a shortcut.

67
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,520
Next time, if you don't show up,

68
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,320
don't make excuses.

69
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,360
[It seems]

70
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:08,320
[he hasn't fully trusted me yet.]

71
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:10,920
[I need to keep trying.]

72
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,600
Yan,

73
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:23,040
this is a new model of phone.

74
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,280
It's very expensive.

75
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:26,160
Who gave it to you?

76
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:32,040
Is it Mr. Fu?

77
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,360
He came to you several times

78
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:37,040
and gave you such a valuable gift.

79
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:39,120
Does he have a crush on you?

80
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:47,000
If he really has a crush on me,

81
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,760
it will be more convenient.

82
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:53,200
I don't have your contact information yet.

83
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:54,880
Could you leave me your number?

84
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,320
Brother Fu,

85
00:09:58,640 --> 00:09:59,520
well,

86
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:01,840
you should know

87
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:04,560
that when a phone receives a call or a message,

88
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:06,040
it will ring, right?

89
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:16,240
The GPS device in her phone,

90
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:18,240
is it confirmed to be working properly?

91
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,000
Boss,

92
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,720
do you still suspect she's from IPCO?

93
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:35,480
Tomorrow afternoon at 3 o'clock,

94
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:37,200
come to the Silver Light Hall.

95
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,720
Let Tian Yan go to the reception room.

96
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,080
Mrs. Shi is waiting.

97
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:56,800
Okay.

98
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,160
You come to my place to see the goods.

99
00:10:59,160 --> 00:11:00,600
It's really an honor.

100
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,600
Look who I've called for you.

101
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:04,600
Hey.

102
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:06,040
You're here.

103
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:06,960
Mrs. Shi.

104
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:10,040
Mrs. Shi,

105
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,400
you look stunning today.

106
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,400
Oh,

107
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:13,440
Boss Fu,

108
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:14,640
you really know how to treat your clients.

109
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,040
No wonder your business is booming.

110
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:18,760
This girl is talented,

111
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:19,760
has guts,

112
00:11:19,760 --> 00:11:20,960
and good luck.

113
00:11:21,040 --> 00:11:21,800
I like her.

114
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:23,280
Then let her talk to you.

115
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:24,640
I'll send someone to get the goods.

116
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:29,520
Come on.

117
00:11:30,560 --> 00:11:31,960
I didn't get a chance to ask you last time.

118
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:33,960
How's it going?

119
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,320
What stage are you at?

120
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:38,480
What stage?

121
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,440
You and Mr. Fu.

122
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,120
No.

123
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,120
You misunderstood.

124
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:45,320
Mr. Fu and I

125
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,520
just met by chance.

126
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:47,800
He helped me a few times.

127
00:11:47,800 --> 00:11:48,920
I'm very grateful to him.

128
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:50,320
And

129
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,160
he said...

130
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,840
Listen,

131
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:54,880
no man would repeatedly

132
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:56,520
help a woman for no reason.

133
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,440
The way he looks at you,

134
00:11:58,560 --> 00:12:00,080
he definitely has feelings for you.

135
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:04,080
Do you...

136
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,200
really think so?

137
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:10,000
Boss Fu

138
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,120
is quite obvious.

139
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,600
You'll see.

140
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:14,040
He may be tough on the outside,

141
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,000
but he's practically

142
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:16,560
ready to give you his heart.

143
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:27,280
The way you've managed

144
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:29,720
the Silver Light Hall

145
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:32,040
is quite impressive.

146
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:34,680
Mom.

147
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:37,320
I'm the head of the Silver Light Hall.

148
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:40,080
I have to keep up appearances.

149
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:42,000
But

150
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:44,720
you're from the streets.

151
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:47,400
You'll never be a proper leader.

152
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:48,720
Dad's not well.

153
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:49,880
I'll come by more often.

154
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,320
Just in case

155
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:53,680
you mess things up.

156
00:12:56,680 --> 00:12:58,240
What brings you two here

157
00:12:58,720 --> 00:12:59,520
today?

158
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:02,160
Now that Shi Qing is back,

159
00:13:02,520 --> 00:13:03,840
he should get familiar

160
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,400
with the family business.

161
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:07,720
After all,

162
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,200
only when the name is right can the speech be smooth.

163
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,280
Back then, your mother

164
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,640
was confused

165
00:13:13,760 --> 00:13:14,520
and did some

166
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:15,880
things she shouldn't have done.

167
00:13:16,640 --> 00:13:17,600
but in the end,

168
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:19,640
she paid for her crimes.

169
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:22,040
She got what she deserved,

170
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:23,680
and died for a worthy cause.

171
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,520
You should be grateful

172
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:26,720
for what you have today,

173
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,600
and stay in your place.

174
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:30,280
Don't be like your mother,

175
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:32,240
who had ambitions beyond her station,

176
00:13:32,560 --> 00:13:34,120
and a fate as fragile as paper.

177
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:35,880
In the end,

178
00:13:35,880 --> 00:13:38,080
she didn't even get

179
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:40,080
a proper title.

180
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:44,400
The reputation of the Silver Light Hall

181
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,760
and the family

182
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:49,520
is more important than anyone's gains and losses.

183
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,880
My mother

184
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:53,080
sacrificed herself for the family.

185
00:13:57,920 --> 00:13:58,440
Ah.

186
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:01,440
Excuse me.

187
00:14:01,920 --> 00:14:04,680
Could you please ask Mrs. Shi to the reception room?

188
00:14:05,560 --> 00:14:06,680
Mr. Fu said

189
00:14:06,760 --> 00:14:08,120
to invite her to the front hall to view the goods.

190
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:08,960
Okay.

191
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:09,680
Got it.

192
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:10,400
Thank you.

193
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:19,120
Mr. Fu, I'm sorry.

194
00:14:19,160 --> 00:14:20,280
I'm sorry.

195
00:14:24,160 --> 00:14:26,760
I just wanted to bring tea to the guest.

196
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:28,760
But I went to the wrong place.

197
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:29,800
I got lost.

198
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:31,040
How rude!

199
00:14:31,280 --> 00:14:33,440
Can't you see your master is talking?

200
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:35,400
This is my guest.

201
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:36,800
No wonder.

202
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:38,880
A mother who can't be seen in public.

203
00:14:39,120 --> 00:14:40,600
An illegitimate child who shouldn't have been born.

204
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,680
Even the guest

205
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:45,440
is so rude.

206
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,440
The family education

207
00:14:56,880 --> 00:14:57,920
is interesting.

208
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:58,720
Mrs. Shi.

209
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:02,000
Mrs. Shi.

210
00:15:02,160 --> 00:15:02,920
What a coincidence.

211
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:05,960
I was just about to visit you these days

212
00:15:06,160 --> 00:15:07,240
to discuss cooperation.

213
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,640
A while ago,

214
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:16,400
I had the cooperation documents sent to you.

215
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:17,520
Have you had a chance to review them?

216
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:21,960
In a family,

217
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:22,720
there are always some

218
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:25,360
undesirable people and situations.

219
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:27,480
that need constant correction.

220
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,280
I apologize for any embarrassment.

221
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:30,680
So,

222
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:33,400
Lady Fan was just correcting me, huh?

223
00:15:36,680 --> 00:15:38,200
I, Shi Pengyue,

224
00:15:38,560 --> 00:15:40,720
am the fourth child in my family,

225
00:15:42,520 --> 00:15:43,480
an illegitimate daughter.

226
00:15:44,560 --> 00:15:46,240
Oh, you mean the "wild child"

227
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:48,760
who shouldn't have been born.

228
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:50,640
Mrs. Shi,

229
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:51,680
you've misunderstood.

230
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:53,440
We absolutely didn't mean that.

231
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:54,760
This is all...

232
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,280
This is all family matters.

233
00:15:57,560 --> 00:15:58,680
We'll sort it out at home.

234
00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:00,480
It doesn't affect our business cooperation.

235
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:01,520
Ah,

236
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:02,720
Boss Fu,

237
00:16:02,760 --> 00:16:03,800
why is your family

238
00:16:03,800 --> 00:16:05,400
such a mess?

239
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:07,200
It makes me a bit uneasy.

240
00:16:09,640 --> 00:16:11,920
My father has long wanted to cooperate with Minghui Pavilion.

241
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:14,320
I finally invited Mrs. Shi here today.

242
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:16,040
What are you two doing?

243
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:19,960
Mrs. Shi,

244
00:16:20,040 --> 00:16:20,680
just now,

245
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:21,840
I was being foolish.

246
00:16:21,920 --> 00:16:23,240
I didn't think before I spoke.

247
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,560
I was just talking nonsense.

248
00:16:24,760 --> 00:16:26,520
Please don't take it to heart.

249
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:28,680
I'll make it up to you right away.

250
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:30,640
You are

251
00:16:30,640 --> 00:16:32,080
such a capable person.

252
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:33,520
- must be... - Alright.

253
00:16:33,520 --> 00:16:34,360
It's fine.

254
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:35,360
Where's the contract?

255
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,560
We've already signed it last time.

256
00:16:36,880 --> 00:16:39,560
From now on, all the jade business

257
00:16:39,560 --> 00:16:40,880
of my husband and I

258
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:42,240
will be done with the Silver Light Hall.

259
00:16:44,040 --> 00:16:45,160
That's great.

260
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:46,040
Great.

261
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:47,160
From now on,

262
00:16:47,160 --> 00:16:48,080
our Minister Si...

263
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:48,920
However,

264
00:16:50,160 --> 00:16:51,560
I only recognize Boss Fu.

265
00:16:52,680 --> 00:16:55,640
If the Silver Light Hall is taken over by some

266
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:58,560
pretentious nobles in the future,

267
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:01,240
I will unite all members of the Chamber of Commerce

268
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:02,880
to boycott the Silver Light Hall.

269
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:05,240
Boss Fu,

270
00:17:05,520 --> 00:17:06,400
you know that

271
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:07,640
I always

272
00:17:07,680 --> 00:17:08,680
keep my word.

273
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,760
Don't worry, Mrs. Shi.

274
00:17:11,360 --> 00:17:13,120
I'll take good care of myself

275
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:14,520
and be the head of

276
00:17:14,520 --> 00:17:16,600
the Silver Light Hall for a long time.

277
00:17:16,840 --> 00:17:18,080
I'll keep working with

278
00:17:18,360 --> 00:17:19,480
your Minghui Pavilion.

279
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:20,760
Okay.

280
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:22,720
I'll be on my way now.

281
00:17:23,120 --> 00:17:25,200
Next time, I'll bring Jingjing to check out the goods

282
00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:27,400
and we can play mahjong together.

283
00:17:27,440 --> 00:17:28,440
I'll definitely beat both of you.

284
00:17:28,760 --> 00:17:29,440
Take care.

285
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:32,000
See Mrs. Shi off.

286
00:17:33,840 --> 00:17:35,240
You've grown up.

287
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:38,760
You brought a wild woman to set us up.

288
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:42,280
I'll say it one last time.

289
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:48,680
She's my guest.

290
00:17:49,800 --> 00:17:51,000
Father always said

291
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,200
the reputation of the Silver Light Hall

292
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:54,360
and the honor of the family

293
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:56,320
are more important than anyone's gains or losses.

294
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:58,280
I've always believed in this.

295
00:17:59,120 --> 00:18:02,160
